load_annotation_files <- function(output_dir, pattern = "*_eval_measures.tsv") {
    param_files <- Sys.glob(file.path(output_dir, "*", "*_params.tsv"))
    ann_files <- Sys.glob(file.path(output_dir, "*", pattern))
    
    params <- plyr::rbind.fill(lapply(param_files, function(f) {
        params <- fread(f)
        data.frame(root = dirname(f), params)
    }))
    
    anns <- plyr::rbind.fill(lapply(ann_files, function(f) {
        anns <- tryCatch({
            df <- fread(f)
            return(data.frame(root = dirname(f), df))
        }, error = function(e) {
            return(data.frame())
        })
    }))
    
    result <- anns %>% plyr::join(params, by = "root")
    return(result)
}

evaluate_de <- function(eval_measures, measures = c("v_measure", "accuracy", 
    "macro_f1", "micro_f1")) {
    eval_measures <- load_annotation_files(output_dir, pattern = "*_eval_measures.tsv")
    
    eval_measures_markers_de_melted <- eval_measures %>% dplyr::filter(is.na(mapping_type) | 
        mapping_type == "de") %>% dplyr::filter(is.na(gene_set) | gene_set == 
        "markers") %>% reshape2::melt(measure.vars = measures, variable.name = "measure", 
        value.name = "value")
    
    eval_measures_full_de_melted <- eval_measures %>% dplyr::filter(is.na(mapping_type) | 
        mapping_type == "de") %>% dplyr::filter(is.na(gene_set) | gene_set == 
        "full") %>% reshape2::melt(measure.vars = measures, variable.name = "measure", 
        value.name = "value")
    
    marker_de_plot <- ggplot(eval_measures_markers_de_melted, aes(x = factor(de_prob), 
        y = value, fill = clustering_method)) + geom_boxplot(outlier.size = -1) + 
        theme_bw() + theme_Publication() + theme_nature() + facet_wrap(~measure, 
        scales = "free", ncol = 1, strip.position = "right") + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, 
        hjust = 1)) + xlab("% genes DE/group") + ylab("Score")
    
    full_de_plot <- ggplot(eval_measures_full_de_melted, aes(x = factor(de_prob), 
        y = value, fill = clustering_method)) + geom_boxplot(outlier.size = -1) + 
        theme_bw() + theme_Publication() + theme_nature() + facet_wrap(~measure, 
        scales = "free", ncol = 1, strip.position = "right") + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, 
        hjust = 1)) + xlab("% genes DE/group") + ylab("Score")
    
    return(list(marker_plot = marker_de_plot, full_plot = full_de_plot))
}
